While learning about cybercrime, I was surprised to see how easily people become victims of UPI scams due to a lack of awareness. Many people mistakenly believe that entering their UPI PIN helps them receive money, which is not true at all.

Through this task, I realized how important it is to stay cautious during online transactions. One habit I plan to follow is never approving unknown payment requests or scanning unfamiliar QR codes. I also want to raise awareness among my friends and family so they can stay safe from such cyber frauds.
